      "line_index": 342,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "c0a55c5b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "何度も熱いモノが肉竿を駆け上がる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "345.0",
      "line_index": 345,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "27960117",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "さっきよりいっぱい出てる♥　お腹熱いよぉ……♥　はぁぁぁ～♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "347.0",
      "line_index": 347,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5da37912",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "瞳はとろんと蕩け、口の端からヨダレを垂らしながら、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "347.2",
      "line_index": 347,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "5da37912",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "幸せそうにうっとりするルミナ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "349.0",
      "line_index": 349,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5f4cd1c8",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "俺だけに見せてくれるルミナのそんな姿に、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "349.2",
      "line_index": 349,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "5f4cd1c8",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "心が幸福感で満たされていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "352.0",
      "line_index": 352,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b6bcc88f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "愛する人とのエッチ……♥　さいこう……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "352.2",
      "line_index": 352,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "b6bcc88f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "強引なあなたも、素敵……♥　ますます惚れちゃった……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "355.0",
      "line_index": 355,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c3f37199",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "俺もますますルミナのこと……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "358.0",
      "line_index": 358,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d42e061",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "頬をそっと撫でると、幸せそうに微笑むルミナ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "359.0",
      "line_index": 359,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b670bca3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ルミナと一つに、エッチして良かった、心の底からそう思う。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "362.0",
      "line_index": 362,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5c0daad5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "えへへ……大好き、だよ……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "365.0",
      "line_index": 365,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "73f4539f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "──ルミナっ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "368.0",
      "line_index": 368,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "feeedbd5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "俺の身体に倒れ込むルミナ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "369.0",
      "line_index": 369,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "61e8256b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "いきなりのことで慌ててしまうも、ルミナは笑顔でこちらに顔を向ける。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "372.0",
      "line_index": 372,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f1a58a73",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "身体に力入らなくなっちゃった……♥　ごめんね、重くない……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "375.0",
      "line_index": 375,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5635f5c6",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "い、いや、全然重くないよ。それよりいきなり倒れて心配しちゃったよ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "379.0",
      "line_index": 379,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5f9c09f2",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "心配かけてごめんね……♥　ああ、あなたの胸、大きくてすごく安心できる……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "382.0",
      "line_index": 382,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "69c26891",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "今日はあなたから離れたくない……ずっと一緒にいたい……ダメ……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "385.0",
      "line_index": 385,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "53c9eb81",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "いや、全然構わないよ。俺もルミナと別れるのは名残惜しいし……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "388.0",
      "line_index": 388,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ec4d684",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ルミナの小さな身体をそっと抱きしめると、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "388.2",
      "line_index": 388,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "ec4d684",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "幸せそうに目を閉じるルミナ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "389.0",
      "line_index": 389,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6c7dd233",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "俺達は互いのぬくもりを感じながら、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "389.2",
      "line_index": 389,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "6c7dd233",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そのまま眠りにつくのであった。",
      "zh": ""
    }
  ]
}
